Package <Unnamed>

Class Summary
Planet The representation of a planet, defined by its mass, radius, velocity, and Ellipse
SolarSystem The Solar System itself, it holds all the planets and calculates force to determine the new velocity and position of each planet
SolarSystemComponent The component for the simulation, handles graphics and keyboard/mouse events
SolarSystemFrame The Frame for the simulation
SolarSystemViewer The main viewer class
Vector2D A class to store public x and y values for ease of use.
